OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers or
OL,6,Flonger spells of rain will spread in
OL,7,Fthrough the evening and overnight, the
OL,8,Frain heavy at times. It will be rather
OL,9,Fwindy around the coasts.
OL,10,
OL,11,CThursday:FBright or sunny spells and
OL,12,Fscattered showers. Becoming dry for a
OL,13,Ftime in the evening as showers fade
OL,14,Fout before cloud and rain arrive
OL,15,Fovernight. Breezy around the coast.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FCloud
OL,18,Fand rain clear east Friday morning,
OL,19,Fwith bright spells and showers
OL,20,Ffollowing. Bright spells and showers
OL,21,Fon Saturday. Dry and bright on Sunday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
